---
// Steps.astro
---

<section class="steps-section bg-watermark">
  <div class="container steps-container">
    <!-- Coluna de Texto -->
    <div class="steps-content">
      <h2 class="steps-title">
        Seus planos impecáveis, do primeiro encontro ao brinde final.
      </h2>
      <p class="steps-text">
        Da concepção à execução, cada etapa é pensada para garantir fluidez, controle e consistência em toda a experiência.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Coluna de Imagem / Gráfico -->
    <div class="steps-image-wrapper">
      <!-- IMG: processos-impecaveis -->
      <img 
        src="/images/processos-impecaveis.jpg" 
        alt="Processo e planejamento - Múltipla Eventos" 
        class="steps-img" 
        loading="lazy"
        data-placeholder="processos-impecaveis"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .steps-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .steps-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .steps-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .steps-section .steps-text {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #0A0706;
  }

  .steps-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border: 1px solid rgba(185, 142, 117, 0.08);
    transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .steps-image-wrapper:hover {
    transform: scale(1.01);
  }

  .steps-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .steps-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .steps-image-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps-section {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    }
  }
</style>
